        "operationId": "updateWebinar",
        "summary": "Update webinar",
        "description": "Updates a webinar. The call requires at least one of the parameters in the request body. The request completely replaces the existing session, series, or sequence and so must include the full definition of each as for the Create call. Set notifyParticipants=true to send update emails to registrants.\n",
        "parameters": [
